---
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>About — Chirag Dodiya, Senior Bubble Developer</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Learn about Chirag Dodiya: Senior Bubble Developer, no-code expert, and SaaS builder for startups and founders." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="About — Chirag Dodiya, Senior Bubble Developer" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Discover Chirag Dodiya’s background, Bubble expertise, and approach to building world-class no-code web apps and automations." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="profile" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  </head>

  <body class="min-h-screen bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 flex flex-col">
    <Navbar />

    <main class="flex flex-1 flex-col items-center px-4 py-16 lg:py-28">
      <section class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 p-8 text-center">
        <img
          src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1742127779993550848/-qVtGtZo_400x400.jpg"
          alt="Chirag Dodiya profile"
          class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 border-4 border-green-500 shadow-lg object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-2">
          About Chirag Dodiya
          <span class="block text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 text-xl font-semibold mt-1">Senior Bubble Developer</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          I’m Chirag—an entrepreneur, product builder, and <span class="font-semibold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">senior Bubble developer</span> with 7+ years in the web space. My mission: help ambitious founders and teams launch faster with scalable, production-quality no-code apps.
        </p>
        <div class="text-left text-base mb-8">
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200 space-y-3">
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold text-green-700 dark:text-green-400">Expertise:</span> MVPs, SaaS platforms, custom dashboards, workflow automations, and third-party integrations—all built on Bubble.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold text-green-700 dark:text-green-400">Process:</span> User-focused design, data architecture done right, rapid prototyping, transparent communication, and shipping on time—every time.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-semibold text-green-700 dark:text-green-400">Why Bubble:</span> It empowers rapid iteration and full-stack capability with speed. No code, no compromise.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400">How I Can Help</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">Whether you need an MVP, to automate internal ops, or launch a SaaS, I’ll help you turn your ideas into robust, scalable digital products using Bubble.</p>
          <ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-3">
            <li class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-semibold text-sm">Bubble App Builds</li>
            <li class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-semibold text-sm">API/Workflow Integration</li>
            <li class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-semibold text-sm">No-Code Coaching</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Let’s Connect</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6">
            Interested in building with Bubble or upgrading your digital stack?
            Reach out for a consultation—I’m open to new projects, partnerships, or just a chat about the future of no-code!
          </p>
          <a
            href="mailto:chirag@dodiya.in"
            class="inline-block px-7 py-3 bg-green-700 dark:bg-green-500 text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition hover:bg-green-800 dark:hover:bg-green-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-green-300 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Contact Chirag
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>